start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572646534"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/o8imCgTodvY?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/o8imCgTodvY?si=TnA9XNKWh1sM21ma" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/o8imCgTodvY?si=TnA9XNKWh1sM21ma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31943769&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1888222055683b84cfb3b4c6_61793765"/><published>2025-06-01T00:45:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9bb1577bcccc37e5c2a94e5ecdf5e904</id><title>2選1.....</title><updated>2025-05-29T13:53:34+08:00</updated><author><name>細姐</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-29T13:53:34+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572613679"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572613679"&gt;1）醫院工運送病人返屋企需要體力勞動一至三年合約，辛苦工要輪班但係就穩定唔會受外圍經濟環境影響，人工$19xxx&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;2）大型零售品牌公司文職，朝九晚六/五天工作比較舒服，人工$17xxx&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;兩份人工都高過我之前嗰份，同埋本人諗住做多三/四年就可以半退休只係想搵埋呢幾年錢，想聽下你哋自己會揀邊份&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 細姐 於 2025-5-30 09:29 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31941434&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-29T13:53:34+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9f7b5f0e0f99159ce63d559d98e8da35</id><title>到底個的公司咩心態不停登廣告就係唔請人，唔安排面試？</title><updated>2025-05-28T13:57:48+08:00</updated><author><name>OL公主</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-28T13:57:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572597857"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572597857"&gt;老公失業5個月，佢話已經SEND咗73份CV，但一份工都冇見過！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;佢話見好多公司不停登廣告請人，但就唔會安排人面試！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有幾間公司係老公本行業，本職位，老公勝任有餘，老公重複申請二至三次都冇安排面試！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;到底咩心態不停登廣告就係唔請人，唔面試？&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31940384&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-28T13:57:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>aef9b3d92d58b0ff281daba254c7e883</id><title>想考CPA增值自己，會唔會都係個好選擇？</title><updated>2024-11-27T15:34:54+08:00</updated><author><name>老千蛋白質</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2024-11-27T15:34:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_569866833"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_569866833"&gt;本身喺Inhouse Finance 做咗5年幾嘢，平時做嘢都睇開Financial Report同Forecasting，一路都冇考牌但最近越嚟越覺得，考返個CPA牌會更加幫到自己升上去......&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;不過始終都成30幾歲人，要由頭讀起十幾科，對我嚟講就真係有啲吃力，想問吓有冇方法可以考得快啲？&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31769994&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2024-11-27T15:34:54+08:00</published></entry></feed>